>
	<p>
		Dr. Kathy is a Board Certified Psychiatric Nurse Practitioner, formerly a Registered Nurse 
		with experience in adult, pediatric, and neonatal populations, in both acute and critical care. </p>
	<p>
		Her approach to patient care is inspired by her experience seeking robust and affirmative mental health 
		support for her friends and family members. She feels that strong mental health support 
		is vital for physical health and overall wellbeing.</p>
	<p>
		The resources on this website are intended for use by her patients, in collaboration with 
		interdisciplinary treatment plans, medication management, and psychotherapy. </p>
	<p>
		<h3>Crisis resources include: </h3></p>
	<p>
		<li>Dial 988 for the crisis hotline</li>
		<li>Text Home to 741741 for text crisis support</li>
		<li>Dial 911 for emergency support</li> 
	</p>

